>加兹（Ghazi）在2025年格莱美奖的红地毯上赶上了广告牌的俄罗斯方块凯利和拉尼亚·安夫托斯。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235890555</post-id></item><item><title> Sabrina Carpenter在2025 Grammys上赢得了最佳流行音乐专辑：“我没想到这个”</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/sabrina-carpenter-grammy-best-best-pop-vocal-album-1235890520/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Carl Lamarre]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 03 Feb 2025 02:25:37 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music News]]></category><category><![CDATA[Pop]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235890520 </guid><description><![CDATA[She earned her second win of the night after <em>Short N&#39;Sweet淘汰了Billie Eilish，Taylor Swift，Ariana Grande和Chappell Roan。]>;]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
><a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/sabrina-carpenter/"  >萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）</a>在周日晚上（2月2日）获得了她的<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/t/pop/"  >第二次</a>格莱美奖，这是她2024年的家园项目<em>Short N&#39;Sweet的礼貌。</em>这位“浓缩咖啡”歌手在2025年格莱美颁奖典礼上表达了感激之情。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/04-grammy-trophy-2019-billboard-espanol-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/04-grammy-trophy-2019-billboard-espanol-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="格莱美奖杯" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">这是2025年格莱美颁奖典礼名单（现场更新） </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 02/02/2025 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “我真的没想到这一点，”一位令人惊讶的木匠说，他在当晚早些时候<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/sabrina-carpenter-espresso-please-please-please-2025-grammys-1235890176/"  >演出</a>。 “所有在屏幕上的提名人都是世界上我最喜欢的艺术家，我简直不敢相信我现在在这个房间里被提名。哇。这是我的[第二]格莱美奖，所以我要哭了。”</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Carpenter继续感谢录音学院，她的粉丝，岛屿唱片和她的母亲，她说“将她驱使她参加每一次声乐课”，继续分享她的赞赏。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>卡彭特说：“你们不知道我有多爱你，这张专辑对我意味着什么。”她的声音充满了情感，然后用散发出的“圣经”打断了她令人激动的演讲。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>卡彭特（Carpenter）进入了六个奖项的当晚，包括年度最佳专辑，年度歌曲，年度唱片和最佳新艺术家。如前所述，晚上早些时候，Carpenter在有趣的表演“请请请”和“浓缩咖啡”的表演中打了一拳，在此期间，她提供了一套好莱坞敬业的套装，其中包括众多的服装更换，有趣的Tap例程，一些喜剧片，一些喜剧片和更多的。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>在演出仪式之前，Carpenter赢得了“浓缩咖啡”的最佳流行音乐表演，从比赛中驱逐了碧昂斯，Eilish，Roan和Charli XCX。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235890520</post-id></item><item><title> TEMS谈论赢得最佳非洲表现和更多|格莱美奖2025</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/video/tems-talks-winning-best-best--frican-performance-grammys-2025/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Katie Cao]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 03 Feb 2025 02:20:57 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Billboard]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys 2025]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc_top_video&amp;p=1235890527 </guid><description><![CDATA[Tems caught up with Billboard&#8217;s Tetris Kelly and Rania Aniftos on the 2025 GRAMMYs red carpet. ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Tems在2025 Grammys红地毯上赶上了Billboard的Tetris Kelly和Rania Aniftos。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235890527</post-id></item><item><title>你们展示了比安卡·辛科里（Bianca Censori）的格莱美（Grammys）连衣裙看起来像红地毯</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/ye-bianca-censori-grammys-dress-dress-transparent-photos-photos-photos-1235890427/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ashley Iasimone]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 03 Feb 2025 02:19:49 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys]]></category><category><![CDATA[News]]></category><category><![CDATA[nsfw]]></category><guid ispermalink="false">https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235890427 </guid><description><![CDATA[The "custom couture" dress looks transparent, whether worn or hanging on a wall.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/kanye-west"  >Ye</a>的妻子Bianca Censori穿着的衣服在2025年格莱美奖的红地毯上几乎没有想象力。你们说，这种设计似乎是如此纯粹，以至于在相机上有效地透明了。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>夫妻在格莱美颁奖典礼上，夫妻颁奖典礼上的周日晚上（2月2日）在Instagram上发布了有关这套服装的信息，这对夫妇走过前展览地毯，Censori在那里用一些镜头遮盖了自己的外套。他首先展示了一张悬挂在灰白色/中性墙上的衣服的照片，衣服几乎与之混合在一起。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/taylor-swift-red-carpet-grammy-award-feb-2025-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/taylor-swift-red-carpet-grammy-award-feb-2025-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> 2025年格莱美红地毯：请参阅最佳照片</h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 02/02/2025 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>说唱歌手在美国东部时间晚上8点后不久在他的帐户上出版的说唱歌手<a  href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFl2_7oy-lq/?hl=en"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >说</a>：“定制的高级格莱美连衣裙给我爱我最好的朋友我的妻子，我是我最好的朋友我的妻子。”</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Ye跟进了一组Censori的宝丽来对该作品进行建模。他拍了几枪。他只是将帖子标题为“爱情故事”。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Censori还在<a  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  target="_blank"  href="https://www.instagram.com/bianca.censori/?hl=en"  >Instagram上</a>分享了她格莱美奖的快照，没有字幕。她的照片显示了衣服穿的样子。 （警告：仍然透明。）</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>在格莱美颁奖典礼上的红地毯上，她穿着外套摆姿势，然后完整地展示。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1240" height="1772" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-and-Bianca-Censori-red-carpet-grammy-award-feb-2025-billboard-1240.jpg?w=717" alt="Kanye West和Bianca Censori" class="wp-image-1235890173" srcset="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-and-Bianca-Censori-red-carpet-grammy-award-feb-2025-billboard-1240.jpg 1240w, https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West-and-Bianca-Censori-red-carpet-grammy-award-feb-2025-billboard-1240.jpg?resize=210,300 210w" sizes="(min-width: 87.5rem) 1000px, (min-width: 78.75rem) 681px, (min-width: 48rem) 450px, (max-width: 48rem) 100vw" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Kanye West和Bianca Censori于2025年2月2日在洛杉矶参加了第67届格莱美奖。</figcaption></figure><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> 在发稿时，Censori的帐户是Instagram上唯一关注的帐户。她回来了，只跟随你们。然而，仅在周日的几个小时前，泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）莫名其妙地<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/kanye-west-only-following-taylor-swift-instagram-1235889832/"  >孤独的人跟随了孤独的人</a>。斯威夫特没有回馈青睐。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/04-grammy-trophy-2019-billboard-espanol-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/04-grammy-trophy-2019-billboard-espanol-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="格莱美奖杯" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">这是2025年格莱美颁奖典礼名单（现场更新） </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 02/02/2025 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Ye在2025 Grammys的最佳说唱歌曲中被提名为“嘉年华”的最佳说唱歌曲。 Rich the Kid＆Playboi Carti。赶上格莱美奖获奖者的完整列表， <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/grammys-2025-winners-complete-list-1235889365/"  >在此处</a>进行现场更新。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Ye目前可以在他的<a  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  target="_blank"  href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFl2_7oy-lq/?hl=en"  >Instagram帐户</a>上找到这件衣服的照片。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235890427</post-id></item><item><title> Shaboozey在Hot 100上谈论成功，这是Morgan Wallen合作及更多的潜力|格莱美奖2025</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/video/shaboozey-hot-100-success-potential-morgan-wallen-collaboration-grammys-2025/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Emily Fuentes]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 03 Feb 2025 02:18:02 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Videos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Billboard]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys 2025]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc_top_video&amp;p=1235890537 </guid><description><![CDATA[Shaboozey caught up with Billboard&#8217;s Tetris Kelly and Rania Aniftos on the 2025 GRAMMYs red carpet.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> Shaboozey在2025 Grammys红地毯上赶上了Billboard的Tetris Kelly和Rania Aniftos。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235890537</post-id></item><item><title>查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/chappell-roan-pink-pony-club-2025-grammys-1235890501/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Joe Lynch]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 03 Feb 2025 02:13:52 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235890501 </guid><description><![CDATA[The Grammy-nominated star also spoke out in defense of trans rights on the red carpet. ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
><a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/chappell-roan/"  >查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan</a> ）在2025年格莱美颁奖典礼上获得了六项提名 - 在2月2日晚上（2月2日）晚上登上了舞台，表演了“粉红色小马俱乐部”，<em>这是她的粉碎专辑《 The Rise The Rise The Rise The Rise The Rise The Rise an fall》</em>的最令人难忘的歌曲之一<em>中西部公主。</em> </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/04-grammy-trophy-2019-billboard-espanol-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/04-grammy-trophy-2019-billboard-espanol-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="格莱美奖杯" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">这是2025年格莱美颁奖典礼名单（现场更新） </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 02/02/2025 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>合适的是，罗恩（Roan）以巨大的粉红色小马开始了表演，最终跳下马，击败了酷儿发现国歌，周围是牛仔竞技表演，牛仔竞技队（Rodeo Clowns）执行着乡村和西方风格的唱片，挥舞着山基人，挥舞着山和奔跑。当她到达全喉前的前盘前，尤其是珍妮尔·莫妮（Janelle Monae）的大部分观众与热情一起唱歌。整个事情都是一个怪异的，狡猾的酷儿幻想曲 - 正是我们从罗恩（Roan）期望的那种狂热的乐趣。 “<em>我的小马驹</em>长大了，”表演后诺亚打趣道。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “&#39;粉红色小马俱乐部&#39;是我给洛杉矶的情书，”罗恩在预先展示的部分中谈到这首歌，并指出这座城市“给了我勇气成为自己。”据报道，“粉红色小马俱乐部”的灵感来自她在传奇的Weho Gay Bar The Abbey的时间。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>罗恩（Roan）在Billboard Hot 100命中（第26号峰）的表现远非她对LGBTQ唯一的致敬LGBTQ居住在格莱美奖中。在洛杉矶的Crypto.com竞技场上行走红地毯时，Roan花了一点时间来支持跨性别权利，这些权利受到特朗普总统管理的攻击。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “跨性别者一直存在，他们将永远存在。他们永远不会，无论发生什么情况，都将跨性别的欢乐带走。”罗恩<a  href="https://bsky.app/profile/stereogum.bsky.social/post/3lhablot6zk2b"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://bsky.app/profile/stereogum.bsky.social/post/3lhablot6zk2b"  target="_blank"  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  >说</a>。 “没有跨性别女孩，我不会在这里。只是知道流行音乐正在思考您，并且关心您。我正在尽力为您站起来。”</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235890501</post-id></item><item><title>奥马里恩（Omarion）就他的第一个格莱美奖提名和更多|格莱美奖2025</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/video/omarion-gives-durand-bernarr-advice-on-his-first-first-grammys-nomination-more-grammys-2025/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Katie Cao]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 03 Feb 2025 02:08:57 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Videos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Billboard]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grammys 2025]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc_top_video&amp;p=1235890509 </guid><description><![CDATA[Omarion &#38; Durand Bernarr caught up with Billboard&#8217;s Tetris Kelly and Rania Aniftos on the 2025 GRAMMYs red carpet. ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>奥马里恩（Omarion）和杜兰德·伯纳尔（Durand Bernarr）在2025年格莱美奖的红地毯上赶上了Billboard的Tetris Kelly和Rania Aniftos。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235890509</post-id></item></channel></rss>